snippet.description:
Welcome to Every Parent Teacher Meeting ‚Äî where teachers give feedback, and parents bring the real drama! üßë‚Äçüè´üë®‚Äçüë©‚Äçüë¶üí•
In this hilarious sketch, we dive into the world of the parent-teacher meeting ‚Äî a day feared by students across India! From kids who bring a new ‚Äúuncle‚Äù or ‚Äúaunty‚Äù every time, to gunda students acting innocent in front of teachers, and parents who are more clueless than their own kids ‚Äî we‚Äôve captured every type of PTM madness!
And of course, how can we forget those savage desi parents who roast their own child harder than the teacher ever could? Whether it‚Äôs a parent teacher conference or a casual PTM, one thing's guaranteed: full-on comedy and chaos! ü§£
Relive your school memories and tag that friend whose parents came to school with a full charge!

snippet.title: The Revolutionaries - First Look | Nikkhil Advani |Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh
snippet.description:
Here is the first look for The Revolutionaries, new series coming in 2026.

#TheRevolutionariesOnPrime, #PrimeDay

Starring: Bhuvan Bam, Rohit Saraf, Pratibha Ranta, Gurfateh Pirzada and Jason Shah.
Directed by: Nikkhil Advani
Produced by: Monisha Advani and Madhu Bhojwani

A Emmay Entertainment Production

About:
This first-look offers a glimpse into the upcoming series adapted from Sanjeev Sanyal‚Äôs celebrated and widely acclaimed book, Revolutionaries: The Other Story Of How India Won Its Freedom. The Revolutionaries tells the powerful story of brave young Indian freedom fighters who believed that armed resistance was not just vital but indispensable to ending the British Raj. The series is a stirring tribute to their extraordinary lives, sacrifices, and their unwavering, undying love for their country. Currently on floors, The Revolutionaries is being mounted on a grand scale, with filming underway across multiple locations in India, including Mumbai, Amritsar, Varanasi, Dehradun, and more. The Revolutionaries will premiere exclusively on Prime Video in over 240 countries and territories worldwide in 2026.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages ‚Äì including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal ‚Äì The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video‚Äôs video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures ‚Äì Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho sari duniya hai papi, Nuye thali mannai saafi,
Fer dam bhi lagaya pure 1 tole kaa.
Chhati pe likhaya tera naam mannai sambhoo,
Are hath pe chhapaya trishul bhole ka.
Ho.. banke sanyasi teri gel rahna sai,
Mere sir pe ho hath baba dharde nai tuuuu‚Ä¶
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,
Ho teri saran mai lele‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶.

Ho Karmandal pe lipti ya mala rudraks ki,
Is dhal mai to tera hona chahu suuu.
Babya gelya rakh ke nai uth baith bhole,
Tere damru ki lay mai baba khona chahu suuu.
Ho tere dhorai rakh le nai mannai sambhoo jiiii,
Met de nai mere aaj sare dar tuuu‚Ä¶‚Ä¶..
Ho teri saran mai lele, Ya tu dede mrityu,

Sa rrr matlabi duniya farebi ade log,

Balambiye Sumit ki bhi sun le kailasi,
Ade teri dhal pahada mai yo dera laa liyaaa.
Are maar ke nai ak dusre nai sove saaa,

Ek aisa sanki darinda, jiski cheekhein aur hansi ruh tak ko hila deti hai. 'Sangharsh' mein Ashutosh Rana ne villain ko sirf act nahi kiya, balki poori tarah se jee liya. Is video mein dekhiye Lajja Shankar Pandey ke woh darawne pal jo aaj bhi logon ki ragon mein sahran daal dete hain. ‚ÄòSangharsh‚Äô movie mein Ashutosh Rana ne Lajja Shankar Pandey ke roop mein ek aisa khaufnaak villain play kiya tha, jise dekhkar logon ki raaton ki neend ud gayi thi. Ek pagal dharmik fanatic jo bachchon ki bali dekar moksha paana chahta hai ‚Äî uske junoon, paagalpan aur darr ko Ashutosh Rana ne itni intensity ke saath dikhaya ki unke scenes dekhte hi ronge khade ho jaate hain. Is video mein dekhiye unke sabse scary, intense aur horrifying scenes ka zabardast compilation ‚Äî jo dikhata hai kyun wo Bollywood ke most terrifying villains mein se ek hain.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

snippet.title: My Girlfriend is an Alien : The visit
snippet.description:
So I watched My GF is an Alien a few days ago... and now I fully understand why K-drama fans behave the way they do. No offense, but this felt like watching a Chinese Sanjay Singhania fall for a girl with the weirdest fantasy ever.

Was it brainrot? 100%. Was I entertained? Also 100%.

What‚Äôs even crazier ‚Äî all these Korean, Mandarin, and Chinese dramas are available for FREE on Amazon MX Player‚Ä¶ and in Hindi

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

it.title: BIRYANI DI MONTONE | 3 Ricette COMPLETE PER BIRYANI DI MONTONE ARROSTO DI CAPRA Cucinare in un vi...
it.description: Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato un grandioso biryani di montone in stile arabo usando tre capre intere. Per prima cosa, abbiamo bollito le capre intere in un grande recipiente con spezie per rendere la carne tenera e saporita. Poi, abbiamo arrostito con cura ogni capretto su una grande tawa a fuoco diretto di legna da ardere, aggiungendo uno strato affumicato e ricco di sapore. Dopo la cottura, abbiamo guarnito il succoso montone con riso basmati aromatico, masala macinati a mano e spezie tradizionali. Questo enorme biryani √® stato cotto lentamente alla perfezione e condiviso durante una festa di villaggio. Un perfetto mix di biryani di montone affumicato, piccante e tenero, con un tocco arabo.

id.title: Biryani Daging Kambing | 3 Resep Biryani Daging Kambing Panggang Utuh | Masakan Desa | Biryani Arab
id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Pertama, kami merebus seluruh kambing dalam wadah besar berisi bumbu agar dagingnya empuk dan beraroma. Kemudian, kami memanggang setiap kambing dengan hati-hati di atas tawa besar di atas api kayu bakar langsung, menambahkan lapisan rasa berasap yang kaya. Setelah dipanggang, kami melapisi daging kambing yang empuk dengan nasi basmati yang harum, bumbu masala giling tangan, dan rempah-rempah tradisional. Biryani besar ini dimasak perlahan hingga sempurna dan dinikmati bersama dalam pesta desa. Perpaduan sempurna biryani daging kambing berasap, pedas, dan empuk dengan sentuhan Arab.

snippet.description:
#YeRishtaKyaKehelataHai #YRKKH #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #abhira #armaan 

*Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai* is a long-running Indian television drama that explores family relationships, love, and societal dynamics through its evolving storylines. The show, which began with Akshara and Naitik's journey, has progressed through generations, maintaining its core theme of familial bonds. In the current track, the focus has shifted to a new generation, highlighting the lives of Abhira (the union of Abhimanyu and Akshara's legacy), Armaan, and Ruhi. These characters navigate their relationships, ambitions, and the challenges of their lineage while upholding the values of the Goenka and Birla families. The blend of drama, emotions, and cultural nuances continues to resonate with viewers, ensuring its enduring popularity.

Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi

Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku

Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Morni Official Music Video | Darshan Raval | Divyansha K | Siddharth A B| Naushad Khan | Indie Music
snippet.description:
"Morni" keeps the beloved tradition alive! Every monsoon, Darshan Raval gifts his fans a rain-soaked melody, and this year is no different. Sung and composed by Darshan himself, with heartfelt lyrics by Siddharth A. Bhavsar and Darshan Raval, the song captures the innocence of two hearts setting out on a beautiful, unknown journey of love. With a music video that reflects the charm of first monsoon romance, Morni is a promise fulfilled, and a memory waiting to be made.

Singer - Composer : Darshan Raval 
Lyrics : Siddharth Amit Bhavsar & Darshan Raval 
Music Produced & Arranged by Siddharth Amit Bhavsar

snippet.title: Discharge from hospitalüë∂üèªüè•| Adnaan07
snippet.description: A Day Full of Emotions & Celebrations! In this special vlog, we bring you heartfelt moments as my wife and our newborn baby finally get discharged from the hospital! The most emotional part? My mom (our baby's grandma) hasn't seen him yet and is SO EXCITED to meet her grandson for the first time-her reactions are priceless! But the day doesn't end there! As part of our Islamic tradition, we perform aqiqah for our little one, and that means a trip to Deonar Bakra Mandi with my close friends to pick the perfect goat! It's a fun, chaotic, and memorable experience you don't want to miss! Join us in this beautiful journey of love, faith, and family bonding. Don't forget to Like, Share, and Subscribe for more heartfelt vlogs! Turn on notifications so you never miss an update! #newbornbaby  #haqiqa  #familytime  #deonarbakramandi  #islamictraditions
